        <p class="feature-description">All our supplements are manufactured in GMP-certified facilities in the UK using the highest quality raw materials.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Third-Party Tested</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">Every batch is independently tested for purity, potency, and safety. We publish all certificates of analysis for full transparency.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
